'''Future Prophecies''' are Richard Animashaun Thomas and Tony Anthun, a [[drum and bass]] duo from [[Norway]]. Between 1999 and 2006, they released over twenty singles on various labels, including Dj Fresh & Adam F´s label Breakbeat Kaos, Rob Playford´s Moving Shadow, and [[Teebee]]'s influential [[Subtitles Recordings]]. In 2005, they released their first album, ''Warlords Rising'', on Subtitles Ivinyl only) & [[Beatservice]], and a [[mix album]] of their singles catalog, ''Raw'', on [[Outbreak Records (UK)|Outbreak]].

Their live performances combine [[deejaying]] with drums, saxophone, and other live instrumentation (called ''hybrid session'').

