The '''Gambia Civil Aviation Authority''' ('''GCAA''') is the [[civil aviation authority]] of [[The Gambia]]. The agency head office is located at [[Banjul International Airport]] in [[Banjul]].<ref>"[http://www.gambia.gm/gcaa/Forms/adobe%20version/Application%20for%20Flight%20Permit.pdf APPLICATION FOR A FLIGHT PERMIT]." ([https://www.webcitation.org/6E0rWXeU9?url=http://www.gambia.gm/gcaa/Forms/adobe%20version/Application%20for%20Flight%20Permit.pdf Archive]) Gambia Civil Aviation Authority. Retrieved on 28 January 2013. "THE GAMBIA CIVIL AVIATION AUTHORITY BANJUL INTERNATIONAL AIRPORT P.O. BOX 285 BANJUL, THE GAMBIA"</ref>
